{
  "texts": [
    "The third paradigm, agentic chatbots, emerged in December 2024.",
    "It synthesizes fluent language generation, reasoning and autonomous action.",
    "Agentic systems can plan sequences of operations, actively gather information, and adapt their strategies based on what they discover.",
    "For economists, this means AI systems that don't just respond to questions but actively investigate them-a shift from reactive tools to proactive research partners.Breakthrough Agents: Deep Research and Claude Code Perhaps no capability better illustrates the potential (and limitations) of AI agents for research than Deep Research systems.",
    "As described in Section 3, these systems employ multi-agent architectures to process and synthesize hundreds of sources in minutes, producing comprehensive research reports with accurate citations."
  ]
}